Definition: in harmony with the spirit of particular persons or occasion
Example: a decent burial;  We have come to dedicate a portion of that field...It is altogether fitting and proper that we should do this
Synonyms: noun, attribute, fittingness, decent, in, harmony, with, the, spirit, of, particular, persons, or, occasion, a, burial, We, have, come, to, dedicate, portion, that, field, It, is, altogether, and, proper, we, should, do, this
Category: adj.all
